# Laravel Email Templates for Job Management System

## 1. Application Confirmation (Client/Candidate)

**File: `resources/views/emails/application-confirmation.blade.php`**

```blade
@component('mail::message')
# Application Confirmation

Hi {{ $candidate['fullName'] }},

Thank you for applying for the **{{ $position }}** position at {{ config('app.name') }}!

We've successfully received your application. Here are the details:

@component('mail::panel')
**Application Details**
- **Position Applied:** {{ $position }}
- **Application Date:** {{ $appliedDate }}
- **Application ID:** {{ $applicationId }}
@endcomponent

## Next Steps

Our hiring team will review your application carefully. You can expect to hear back from us within **5-7 business days**. 

In the meantime, you can:
- Track your application status by [clicking here]({{ $trackingLink }})
- Update your profile information
- Apply for other open positions

@component('mail::button', ['url' => $trackingLink, 'color' => 'primary'])
Track Your Application
@endcomponent

If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us at [{{ config('mail.from.address') }}](mailto:{{ config('mail.from.address') }}).

Best regards,  
**{{ config('app.name') }} - Hiring Team**

@slot('footer')
@component('mail::footer')
Â© {{ date('Y') }} {{ config('app.name') }}. All rights reserved.
@endcomponent
@endslot
@endcomponent
```

