## 4. Application Status Update (Candidate)

**File: `resources/views/emails/application-status-update.blade.php`**

```blade
@component('mail::message')
# Application Status Update

Hi {{ $candidate['fullName'] }},

We wanted to keep you updated on your application for the **{{ $position }}** position.

@component('mail::panel')
**Current Status:** 
# {{ strtoupper($status) }}

@if($status === 'reviewing')
- Your application is currently under review by our hiring team.
- We'll contact you within 3-5 business days.
@elseif($status === 'interview_scheduled')
- Congratulations! You've been selected for an interview.
- Interview Details: {{ $interviewDate }} at {{ $interviewTime }}
@elseif($status === 'rejected')
- Thank you for your interest. Unfortunately, we've decided to move forward with other candidates at this time.
- We encourage you to apply for future positions that match your profile.
@elseif($status === 'selected')
- Great news! You've been selected for this position!
- Our HR team will be in touch shortly with next steps and offer details.
@endif
@endcomponent

@if($status !== 'rejected')
@component('mail::button', ['url' => $trackingLink, 'color' => 'primary'])
View Application
@endcomponent
@endif

If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at [{{ config('mail.from.address') }}](mailto:{{ config('mail.from.address') }}).

Best regards,  
**{{ config('app.name') }} - Recruiting Team**

@slot('footer')
@component('mail::footer')
Â© {{ date('Y') }} {{ config('app.name') }}
@endcomponent
@endslot
@endcomponent
```

